# 10. Edge Cases

### Only one valid substring

```
abc

Answer = 1
```

---

### Same character repeated

```
aaacb

Answer = 3
```

---

### Characters appear very late

```
aaaaabbbbbc
```

Only after seeing `c` do valid substrings start getting counted.

---

### Minimum length

```
length = 3
```

Works correctly.

